description: Brinova Fastigheter AB engages in the investment, development, management, and marketing of real properties. The company is headquartered in Helsingborg, Skane and currently employs 41 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2016-09-30. The firm is engaged in construction and management of public, community buildings and rental housing in southern Sweden. The firm operates more than 40 properties with a total of over 130 000 square meters. The firm's properties are located in Kristianstad, Hassleholm, Landskrona, Malmo, Lund, Ahus, Vellinge and Karlskrona, among others.
name: Brinova Fastigheter AB (publ)
